{"tid":1295714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：我是非常理解青年人點解要咁做，但我要話你知衝擊係做錯。","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:55:04.000Z","uid":219007,"like":11,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6dbd029c080ee10234cc06e549695e7f90332018","tid":1295714,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L2Xg-CHoolU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL2Xg-CHoolU&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4Vze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=1b236a38\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L2Xg-CHoolU</a><br />\n<br />\n我是非常理解青年人點解要咁做，但我要話你知衝擊係做錯，呢個同年紀世代冇關，錯就錯。<br />\n<br />\n衝擊立法會得到的結果就是大律師公會已讉責佔領立法會，其他國際勢力包括歐盟亦表明暴力衝擊立法會只是少數，和平是多數，這就證明衝擊行為不受國際支持。<br />\n<br />\n為衝擊被捕的抗爭者作法律支援是可以，原因是可盡量減低坐監機會或減少坐監年期。 但若在行動為衝擊行為作後援就是不負責任，因為咁樣都是鼓勵人去死。"},{"pid":"16692750875b50af9c8622a31496894aab5a30f8","tid":1295714,"uid":11143,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"114a2a4af10e9afc5fd42978f26358156386bca0","tid":1295714,"uid":60668,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山"},{"pid":"06a389358a2269f6aa1a9aa7b6df73af3f4247bc","tid":1295714,"uid":37232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"唔應燒山post去政事台"},{"pid":"b8525bbbc3cbaf58ba5c4257e7cae7dc9cc09609","tid":1295714,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"[英文速譯] 綜合大量警察嚴重違規行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8af725fa81f7ade78b16c2b714dbcda7f5403df9","tid":1295714,"uid":37232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔<span style=\"color: red;\">該</span>燒山post去政事台</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9bc61873c7529c5065a1c74d99b8fd24f02db629","tid":1295714,"uid"